                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" 
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#question-two"
                   >
                    Is it authorised organisation?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="question-two" class="accordion-collapse collapse" 
                 data-bs-parent="#questions">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes, we are working for children rights from past many years.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" 
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#question-three"
                   >
                    Can I volunteer for TheyNeedUs organisation?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="question-three" class="accordion-collapse collapse" 
                 data-bs-parent="#questions">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes. syou can contact any one of our volunteers, they will help you in further processing.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>
    </div>
</section>
